name: Doutzen Kroes
description:
Dutch-Frisian photomodel and ex-Victoria's Secret Angel Doutzen Kroes. Probably not widely known, but I think her face definitely has something to it.

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. Some elements are a tad overbaked, but prompting for (Koh_DoutzenKroes:0.99) or playing around with advanced prompting such as [a blonde dutch woman:Koh_DoutzenKroes:0.75] mitigates this.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
